    "is_free": false,
    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3237260/extras/5e1f3aff5bb164ea6cfba80267971449.webp?t=1750132447\" width=617 height=34 /></span>CineSim offers an immersive 3D environment that allows you explore the world of media production. Want to practice lighting a scene, designing a set, or framing the perfect shot? With CineSim, you can do all that and more! Whether you're new to media production or looking to enhance your skills, CineSim provides an intuitive, hands-on platform where you can dive into the world of filmmaking.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Create your own cinematic scenes or explore pre-set templates. CineSim allows you to practice real-world production techniques, all within a stunningly realistic environment powered by Unreal Engine 5—right from your desktop. Unlock a complete cinematic experience with advanced tools, more assets, and full creative control! </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3237260/extras/a3dec57a8028e807d3d64887a7967853.avif?t=1750132447\" width=617 height=347 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3237260/extras/fe0f695ec890cbf09e5d0ca5b7f6f4f0.avif?t=1750132447\" width=617 height=72 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3237260/extras/c45f354188b10a5c22df35ef4b0a697e.webp?t=1750132447\" width=617 height=34 /></span></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Easy-to-navigate design for users of all skill levels.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Drag-and-drop functionality for quick scene creation.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Custom Control Rig to adjust character postures.</strong></p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Import FBX and static mesh to create fully customized scenes.</strong></p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3237260/extras/e7fe396bfcb74b418bf73364c0190e4f.webp?t=1750132447\" width=617 height=34 /></span></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >High-quality 3D visuals powered by Unreal Engine 5.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Real-time previews to instantly view changes.</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3237260/extras/63543b4acdb91d2f58576574d37f40f2.webp?t=1750132447\" width=617 height=34 /></span></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Unlock all pre-set templates: <strong>15</strong> pre-set templates.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Build custom scenes using the &quot;Blank&quot; template.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Access <strong>2000+</strong> assets, including characters, props, facial expressions, and environments.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Customize characters with various facial expressions and actions.</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3237260/extras/fd44a77a00ac36219e8c9390094349be.webp?t=1750132447\" width=617 height=34 /></span></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Full control over camera angles, lens types, and focal lengths.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Preview and adjust camera settings in real-time.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Advanced lighting control for angles and color temperatures.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Full weather control for time of day, sun rotation, and fog density.</strong></p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3237260/extras/52a249948285b9e564e1475b6cd04bb5.webp?t=1750132447\" width=617 height=34 /></span></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Capture high-quality images of your scenes to showcase your work.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Add keyframes to the timeline  to create videos and export as MP4.</strong></p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3237260/extras/af9ce6e63977f16c2cef8021b08125cb.avif?t=1750132447\" width=617 height=72 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Need help or have feedback? </p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Visit our website/youtube channel for comprehensive tutorials.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Email us directly.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Join the discussion on our Steam forum.</p></li></ul>",
